{"tid":1146391,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人期待HBO黎緊播個套由DC Watchmen改篇嘅劇集","createTime":"2019-05-09T08:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T12:34:43.000Z","uid":37759,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"807594a593ed652f0adf84e31c7cfa7d2c75606f","tid":1146391,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:09:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zymgtV99Rko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzymgtV99Rko&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=ba4ebaaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zymgtV99Rko</a><br />\n<br />\nTick tock. WATCHMEN debuts this fall on HBO. <br />\n<br />\nFrom Damon Lindelof and set in an alternate history where &ldquo;superheroes&rdquo; are treated as outlaws, this drama series embraces the nostalgia of the original groundbreaking graphic novel of the same name while attempting to break new ground of its own. <br />\n<br />\nThe cast includes Regina King, Jeremy Irons, Don Johnson, Jean Smart, Tim Blake Nelson, Louis Gossett Jr., Yahya Abdul-Mateen II, Hong Chau, Andrew Howard, Tom Mison, Frances Fisher, Jacob Ming-Trent, Sara Vickers, Dylan Schombing, and James Wolk. <br />\n<br />\nWATCHMEN is based on the graphic novel co-created and illustrated by Dave Gibbons and published by DC."},{"pid":"79730b236c57e56d48e3f5cca4881da4ec1e2024","tid":1146391,"uid":24788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:02:58.000Z","msg":"電影好正<br />\n重睇咗幾次"},{"pid":"5ad7a2a4f0bb12813db379ff202e69dbe0509068","tid":1146391,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:08:10.000Z","msg":"時間點係Dr Manhattan 出現前??"},{"pid":"578992acc396c1185577b15b751547f63cdb2aa2","tid":1146391,"uid":238051,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmAOYEO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://